{% block body %}
    <h1 class= "fs-54 dawning">Recipe <span class= "fs-32 arvo">card :</span></h1>

    <div class="p-3 mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class= "fs-48 bitter  ">Teriyaki chicken bites <span class= "fs-32 arvo"></span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-hidden d-flex justify-content-center">
        <img class="img-fluid align-self-center" src="{{ asset('asset/img/chickenbites.jpg') }}"  alt="Chicken bites">
    </div>

    <div class="row ml-5 wh-100-80 mt-3 d-flex justify-content-end fs-18">
        <img class="icon img-fluid" src="{{ asset('asset/img/favorites.png') }}" alt="Ajouter la recette aux favoris">
        <div class="texticon  mt-2 ml-1">Add to favorite recipes</div>

        <img class="icon ml-4" src="{{ asset('asset/img/print.png') }}" alt="Imprimer la recette">
        <div class="texticon  mt-2 ml-1">Print</div>

        <img class="icon ml-4" src="{{ asset('asset/img/share.png') }}" alt="Partager la recette">
        <div class="texticon mt-2 ml-1">Share</div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-2 mx-auto text-center mb-0 mt-3">
        <p class="fs-25 fw-bolder text-center mb-0 arvo">Ingredients :</p>
    </div>

    <div class=" mx-auto text-center fs-18 arvo">
        <p class="mb-1 ">
            6 Tbsp Ketchup
        </p>

        <p class="mb-1 ">
            1/3 Cup Apple Cider Vinegar
        </p>

        <p class="mb-1 ">
            1.5 tsp Garlic Powder
        </p>

        <p class="mb-1 ">
            1.5 Tbsp Soy Sauce, low sodium
        </p>

        <p class="mb-1 ">
            1.5 Cup Chicken, boneless, skinless, cut into 1-inch chunks
        </p>

        <p class="mb-1">
            As per need salt and black pepper powder
        </p>

        <p class="mb-1">
            1/2 Cup Cornstarch
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-2 mx-auto text-center arvo fw-bolder arvo mb-0 mt-3">
        <h2 class= "fs-25 mb-0">Make <span>Teriyaki chicken bites</span> :</h2>
    </div>

    <div class=" mx-auto text-center fs-18 arvo d-flex justify-content-center">
        <p class="mb-2 text-center wh-100-50 p-lh">
            Marinate the chicken with salt and black pepper powder.
            Whisk eggs and keep aside.
            Heat oil in a deep frying pan.
            Dip the chicken in cornstarch then again dip the chicken in whisked eggs.
            Slowly drop the chicken in batches in oil and fry till golden brown.
            Drain the chicken on kitchen paper and keep aside.
            Heat the sauce mix in a pan and let it come to a boil.
            Let the sauce boil till the sauce slightly thickens.
            Add the fried chicken pieces to sauce and coat the chicken with sauce well.
            Switch off the flame.
            Garnish with sesame seeds and chopped spring onion greens.
            Serve with rice.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="p-2 mx-auto text-center mb-0 mt-3">
        <p class="fs-25 fw-bolder text-center mb-0 arvo">Video Recipe</p>
    </div>
    <div class=" mx-auto text-center fs-18 arvo d-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 mb-4">
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/r9nyr68SSaE" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
    </div>

    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid wh-100-80 section-bg mt-4 section-bg">
